ptional. It is a number field where you can specify the minimum quantity required for purchase.</p><p><strong>Product Pricing</strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><strong>Maximum Retail Price (MRP) </strong>: This field is required. It is a number field to enter the maximum retail price of the product.</p><p style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><strong>Discount </strong>: This field is required. It is a radio button with two options:</p><p style=\"margin-left:80px;\"><strong>No </strong>: Select this option if no discount is applicable.</p><p style=\"margin-left:80px;\"><strong>Yes </strong>: Select this option if a discount is applicable.</p><p style=\"margin-left:120px;\"><strong>Discount Percentage </strong>: This field is optional and appears only when the <strong>Discount</strong> is set to \"Yes.\" It is a number field with a range of 1-100.</p><p style=\"margin-left:120px;\"><strong>Discount Amount </strong>: This field is optional and appears only when the <strong>Discount</strong> is set to \"Yes.\" It is a number field to specify the fixed discount amount.</p><p><strong>Product Image</strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><strong>Image </strong>: This field is optional. It is a file upload field to upload an image of the product.</p><p><strong>Product Precaution</strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><strong>Precaution </strong>: This field is optional. It is a CK-Editor field to add precautions for the product.</p><p style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><strong>Status </strong>: This field is required. It is a radio button with two options:</p><p style=\"margin-left:80px;\"><strong>Active</strong>: Marks the product precaution as active.</p><p style=\"margin-left:80px;\"><strong>Inactive</strong>: Marks the product precaution as inactive.</p>"
